import { MDBTable, MDBTableBody, MDBTableHead } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit' import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { loadUsersStart } from '../redux/actions' const Home = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const {users} = useSelector(state => state.data) useEffect(() => { dispatch(loadUsersStart()) }, []) return (
First Name. Last Name Gender Email Address Phone Role {users && users.map((item, index) => ( {item.firstName} {item.lastName} {item.gender} {item.email} {item.address} {item.phone} {item.role} ))}
) } export default Home
